<!DOCTYPE html PUBLIC "-//W3C//DTD XHTML 1.0 Transitional//EN" "http://www.w3.org/TR/xhtml1/DTD/xhtml1-transitional.dtd">
<html xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">

<head>
  <meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=UTF-8" />
  <title>CURIOSIKI</title>

  <script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.3.1.min.js" integrity="sha256-FgpCb/KJQlLNfOu91ta32o/NMZxltwRo8QtmkMRdAu8="
    crossorigin="anonymous"></script>

  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Cardo|Montserrat:800i" rel="stylesheet">
  <style type="text/css">
    body {
      margin: 0 0 0 0;
      padding: 0;
      background: #f0f0c3;
      font-family: 'Cardo', sans-serif;
      font-size: calc(3.8xmax + 0.4vmax);

      box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    /*grids ATTRIBUTES*/

    .wrapper {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 16vw 34vw 34vw 16vw);
      ;
      grid-template-rows: [linename1] 6vh [linename2] 12vh [linename3] 64vh [linename4] 12vh [linename5] 6vh;
      position: fixed;
      width: 100vw;
      height: 100vh;
      overflow-x: hidden;
    }


    .SRCH {
      grid-column: 2 / 4;
      grid-row: 2;
    }

    .BODY {
      grid-column: 2 / 4;
      grid-row: 3;
    }

    .SURF {
      grid-column: 2;
      grid-row: 4;
    }

    .DIG {
      grid-column: 3;
      grid-row: 4;
    }

    /*background ATTRIBUTES*/

    .GRIDBOX1 {
      grid-column: 2 / 4;
      grid-row: 2 / 5;
      border: 1vw solid black;
      border-top: none;
      border-bottom: none;
    }

    .GRIDBOX2 {
      grid-column: 2;
      grid-row: 4;
      border: 1vw solid black;
      border-bottom: none;
    }

    .GRIDBOX3 {
      grid-column: 3;
      grid-row: 4;
      border: 1vw solid black;
      border-bottom: none;
    }

    .GRIDBOX4 {
      grid-column: 2 / 4;
      grid-row: 4;
      border: 1vw solid black;
      border-bottom: none;
    }

    .GRIDBOX5 {
      grid-column: 2 / 4;
      grid-row: 2;
      border: 1vw solid black;
      border-bottom: none;
    }

    .HDR {
      grid-column: 1 / 5;
      grid-row: 1 / 2;
      background: #000;
    }

    .FTR {
      grid-column: 1 / 5;
      grid-row: 5 / 6;
      background: #000;


      /*image ATTRIBUTES*/
    }

    .filtered {
      background: #f0f0c3;
    }

    .filtered img {
      mix-blend-mode: multiply;
      -webkit-filter: grayscale(100%) contrast(200%);
      filter: grayscale(100%) contrast(200%);
      opacity: 1;
    }
  </style>
  <script type="text/javascript">
    $(document).ready(function () {
      $("frmSearch").focus();
    });
  </script>
</head>

<body>

  <form method="POST">
    <div class="wrapper" style="height:100vh">

      <div class="GRIDBOX1">
      </div>
      <div class="GRIDBOX2">
      </div>
      <div class="GRIDBOX3">
      </div>
      <div class="GRIDBOX4">
      </div>
      <div class="GRIDBOX5">
      </div>

      <div class="HDR">
      </div>
      <div class="FTR">
      </div>

      <div class="SRCH">

        <input type="text" name="frmSearch" style="font-family:'Montserrat', sans-serif; text-transform: uppercase; font-size: calc(4.6vmin + 0.4vmax); font-weight: bolder; 
    			font-weight: bolder; border: 0pt; background-color: #000; color: #f0f0c3; text-indent: 10px; width: 99%; text-align: center; -webkit-appearance: none; appearance: none;
border-radius: 0;  " value="{{searchterm}}" />


      </div>

      <div class="BODY">
        <div align="center">

          <div style="border:none; width:85%; max-height:55vh ; overflow-y:scroll; overflow-x:hide; min-width: 309px; min-height: 55vh; margin-bottom: 15%; padding-bottom: 2%;">
            <p style="height:auto;">

              <div align="justify">
                <div class="filtered">


                  {{#content}}
                  <p> {{text}}</p>
                  {{/content}} {{^content}}
                  <div align="center">
                    <p>The internet has gifted us with near unlimited access to the entire collective findings of mankind. But for all

the knowledge in the world, how much do we actually learn? </p>

<p>Learning once required research. Rummaging through information and finding the answers along the way. now, The

solution to any question is just one search away. THe Act of finding and digesting information has been replaced

by the instant gratification of a question answered.</p>

<p>the purpose of curiousiki is to reimagine the unlimited content of the internet under the focus of this process

using wikipedia's archives. Surf will allow you to search for your starting point. Dig will take you to your next page.</p>

<p>Surrender yourself to the information super highway and see where it takes you.</p>

<p></p>

<p>Curiousiki was created and developed by George Sarell and Ben Crinion. Copyright 2017.</p>

                  </div>
                  {{/content}}



                </div>
              </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="SURF">
        <div align="center">
          <div style="vertical-align:middle">
            <p>
              <input type="submit" style="font-family:'Montserrat', sans-serif; text-transform: uppercase; font-size: calc(4.6vmin + 0.4vmax); font-weight: bolder;
               border: 0pt; background-color: #000; color: #f0f0c3; width: 15vw; -webkit-appearance: none; appearance: none;
border-radius: 0;  " value="SURF" />
            </p>

          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

  </form>

  
  <div class="DIG">
    <div align="center">
      <div style="vertical-align:middle">
        <p>
          <form method="POST">
            <input type="hidden" name="frmSearch" value="{{dugterm}}" />
            <input type="submit" style="font-family:'Montserrat', sans-serif; text-transform: uppercase; font-size: calc(4.6vmin + 0.4vmax); font-weight: bolder;
               border: 0pt; background-color: #000; color: #f0f0c3; width: 15vw; -webkit-appearance: none; appearance: none;
border-radius: 0;  " value="DIG" />
          </form>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

</body>

</html>
